{"type":"message","id":"afd92961","parentId":"c875bf3e","timestamp":"2026-04-12T02:48:20.065Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-12 02:48:19 UTC] Summarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\nSystem: \nSystem: Focus on:\nSystem: - LLMs\nSystem: - RL\nSystem: - Diffusion models\nSystem: - VLM / robotics\nSystem: \nSystem: Output:\nSystem: - 5 bullet points\nSystem: - Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\nSummarize latest AI news from last 24 hours.\n\nFocus on:\n- LLMs\n- RL\n- Diffusion models\n- VLM / robotics\n\nOutput:\n- 5 bullet points\n- Why it matters (2 lines)\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Sunday, April 12th, 2026 — 2:48 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-12 02:48 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775962100061}}
